45
00:01:54,913 --> 00:01:56,693
Non la indovineremo mai.

46
00:01:58,259 --> 00:02:02,757
The Big Bang Theory s02e21
"The Vegas Renormalization"

47
00:02:02,811 --> 00:02:07,284
Traduzione: DjKabuto, Bally,
Bea-San, TobyDammit

48
00:02:07,330 --> 00:02:10,924
Revisione: Obsidian
Resynch: Basces

49
00:02:21,384 --> 00:02:23,257
